OL,3,CMother's devastation after taking
OL,4,Cepilepsy drug linked to birth defects
OL,6,FAsked if she feels guilty about taking
OL,7,Fsodium valproate, Pamela Dumayne has a
OL,8,Fsimple reply: "Always."
OL,10,FBut like thousands of other women, she
OL,11,Fdid not know about the risks of the
OL,12,Fdrug - used to control epilepsy - when
OL,13,Fshe took it during her seven
OL,14,Fpregnancies.
OL,16,FTwo of her children have died, one at
OL,17,Fthree months old, another aged 14.
OL,19,FThe remaining five have suffered a
OL,20,Frange of health problems.
