OL,3,CMother's devastation after taking
OL,4,Cepilepsy drug linked to birth defects
OL,6,F"The three girls that I had were born
OL,7,Fwith holes in their hearts," she said.
OL,9,F"It's mental health issues as well
OL,10,Fthat they've struggled with. Going
OL,11,Fout, not being able to interact with
OL,12,Frelationships.
OL,14,F"I've questioned it throughout my
OL,15,Fpregnancies, after my pregnancies,
OL,16,Fbecause I was always concerned that I
OL,17,Fwas on medication and I was always
OL,18,Ftold, 'no - valproate is safe'."
OL,20,FIt later emerged that valproate was
OL,21,Fanything but safe.
