OL,3,CMother's devastation after taking
OL,4,Cepilepsy drug linked to birth defects
OL,6,FBut concerns were brushed aside by the
OL,7,Fthen medicines regulator, the
OL,8,FCommittee on Safety of Medicines
OL,9,F(CSM), which advised expectant mothers
OL,10,Fshould not be told about the risks for
OL,11,Ffear for causing "fruitless anxiety".
OL,13,FCampaigners estimate that up to 20
OL,14,Fthousand children may have been
OL,15,Fexposed.
OL,17,FMany suffer from foetal valproate
OL,18,Fspectrum disorder (FVSD), which
OL,19,Fincludes a range of symptoms from
OL,20,Flearning difficulties to heart and
OL,21,Fkidney defects and spina bifida.
