OL,3,CMother's devastation after taking
OL,4,Cepilepsy drug linked to birth defects
OL,6,FIn 2020, the government commissioned a
OL,7,Freport by Baroness Cumberlege, which
OL,8,Flaid bare the problems caused by
OL,9,Fsodium valproate.
OL,11,FTwo years ago, Henrietta Hughes, the
OL,12,FPatient Safety Commissioner for
OL,13,FEngland, published a further report
OL,14,Frecommending that those harmed by
OL,15,Fsodium valproate should be compensated.
OL,17,FThe recommendations included interim
OL,18,Fpayments of up to #100,000 as well as
OL,19,Fregular payments to meet ongoing care
OL,20,Fneeds.
