OL,3,CMother's devastation after taking
OL,4,Cepilepsy drug linked to birth defects
OL,6,FTwo years on though, no payments have
OL,7,Fbeen made.
OL,9,FThe UK Government described the sodium
OL,10,Fvalproate scandal as a "complex
OL,11,Fissue", saying its "priority is to
OL,12,Fensure any response is fair, balanced
OL,13,Fand sensitive to those affected".
OL,15,FIt added: "We are carefully
OL,16,Fconsidering the recommendations within
OL,17,Fthe Hughes Report and we aim to
OL,18,Fprovide an update in due course."
OL,20,FBut Hughes has branded the ongoing
OL,21,Fdelays "a disgrace".
