OL,6,F"Seriously? We've been waiting for the
OL,7,Fresponse to the recommendations from a
OL,8,Freport that I was asked to do by the
OL,9,Fgovernment," she said.
OL,11,F"So as Patient Safety Commissioner,
OL,12,FI'm asking for a rapid response, rapid
OL,13,Faction, and for those patients and
OL,14,Ffamilies who've been harmed to be
OL,15,Ftreated with the dignity and respect
OL,16,Fthat they deserve."
OL,18,FOne of Pam's children, 30-year-old
OL,19,FJoshua, has learning difficulties and
OL,20,Fis unable to live independently.
