OL,6,FShe says a compensation settlement
OL,7,Fwould give her peace of mind as she
OL,8,Flooks to the future.
OL,10,FShe added: "My daughter Katie and her
OL,11,Fpartner will be taking Joshua.
OL,13,F"But he's going to have to have bigger
OL,14,Faccommodation to live with them.
OL,15,FThat's what that money will be used to
OL,16,Fcover.
OL,18,F"The government should pay up. It's
OL,19,Fnot about me, it's about the children.
OL,20,FPay up and give them what they're
OL,21,Fowed."
