OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said that
OL,7,Fresponsibility for a redress scheme
OL,8,Frests with the UK Government.
OL,10,FAdding: "We will continue to press for
OL,11,Fprogress, while ensuring our position
OL,12,Fis clearly understood."
OL,14,FHenrietta Hughes told ITV News that
OL,15,Fshe is continuing to press the
OL,16,FWestminster government over the
OL,17,Fcompensation describing the issue as
OL,18,F"unfinished business".
